r strong directional shields.<br></li><li> Take part in epic fleet battles with Capital Ships duking it out among support ships and <strong>hordes of combat drones</strong>!<br></li><li> Tweak-able Squad AI, <strong>never be caught flying with stupid</strong>, ever.<br></li><li> <strong>Challenging</strong>, but fair Rogue-like-esque gameplay.</li></ul>",
